"We've resolved this; the change should be deployed tonight. \n\nWe now do a client-side validation to display an error on that form. Or, if that somehow gets bypassed, we just replace the characters with an equivalent latin character on the server side before the insert occurs. After all, people can be rather *inventive* in the way they send data to our servers, so we don't want to trust the client code to handle this :-)\n\nThis does introduce a new barrier to internationalization, but that's a bridge for us to cross later on. For now, we only work with English-language documents, so this is acceptable.\n\nWe are looking for other places we can deploy the same validation/replacement. For us, the obvious ones are the Domains collection (used in the DMCA product) and the Users collection.\n\n**To other security researchers:** we don't want to get duplicate reports for every form or Collection that someone might find. We're aware of this issue and are working our way through the list.","automated_response":false,"created_at":"2017-08-17T23:11:49.732Z","updated_at":"2017-08-17T23:11:49.732Z","actor":{"username":"danrubins","cleared":false,"url":"/danrubins","profile_picture_urls":{"medium":"https://profile-photos.hackerone-user-content.com/variants/000/021/222/c1d0d51f40e0c570e2153b6801fe54c997c757f0_original.jpg/fd4ecbe1e3e98c343c7717114485ace2f830f9253103d3cfa7502059868c516c"},"hackerone_triager":false,"hackerone_employee":false},"reporter":{"username":"d4rk_g1rl","url":"/d4rk_g1rl"},"genius_execution_id":null,"team_handle":"legalrobot","actor_is_team_member":true,"actor_is_concealed_member":false},{"id":1937773,"is_internal":false,"editable":false,"type":"Activities::AgreedOnGoingPublic","message":"","automated_response":false,"created_at":"2017-08-17T23:12:31.116Z","updated_at":"2017-08-17T23:12:31.116Z","first_to_agree":true,"actor":{"username":"danrubins","cleared":false,"url":"/danrubins","profile_picture_urls":{"medium":"https://profile-photos.hackerone-user-c